QA/QC

Alignment

Percentage

Feature distribution

Alignment percentage mapped to functional classes of genomic loci. by CollectRNAMetrics of the Picard suite.

Strand Specificity

Non-strand-specific protocol distribution ~ 50%/50%. Strand-specific protocol distribution ~ 99%/1%. by STRAND_SPECIFICITY option of Picard suit.

5 to 3 transcript coverage

Average normalized coverage of top 1000 expressed transcripts by Picard. Usually shows 3 end bias.
All transcripts scaled to a length of 100.
